        Constructor of TokenCardInfo object
        Parameters:
        tokenId - - the card number
        schemeId - - the card type
        expiryDate - - card expiry date; MM/YY format
        cvcRequired - - flag to ask for CVV/CVC when the payment flow starts
        systemAuthRequired - - flag to use System Authentication when cvcRequired=false; this can be false, and no security check will be performed
